modules.description: This module handles MP4 container operations for AAC decoding, providing functions to open files, detect AAC tracks, and manage sample reading. It works with file descriptors, tracks, and audio samples, supporting seeking and metadata extraction. Use it to load and decode specific AAC audio samples from MP4 files, retrieve track information, or extract metadata tags.

This module decodes AAC and AAC+ audio streams, providing functions to initialize a decoder with encoded data, decode raw audio frames, and handle stream synchronization. It operates on raw byte buffers and returns structured audio data as multi-channel float arrays, with support for seeking and error handling. Use it to parse and decode AAC audio from byte streams, extract PCM data for playback or processing, and manage decoder state across fragmented input.
